\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.5 Annual CI Verification
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
CI records shall be actively verified against the deployed asset on an annual basis,
 tied to the physical asset audit conducted under 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:1.12"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
.
 The Verified field in Redmine shall be updated to reflect the date of verification at the time of each annual audit.
 A deployed asset whose Verified date is more than twelve (12) months prior to the current date shall be treated as pending verification for audit purposes.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
The annual physical audit is the systematic sweep for CI record accuracy across the full deployed asset population.
 Work order closure enforcement under Section 6.4 is the continuous mechanism between audits.
 Both mechanisms are complementary and shall operate in parallel.
\end_layout

